68
00:04:21,839 --> 00:04:26,790
You know, they help your team estimate the type of work they're going to complete clarity and common

69
00:04:26,790 --> 00:04:29,010
understanding across the team.

70
00:04:29,250 --> 00:04:31,200
They help your team understand what is going to be built.

71
00:04:31,200 --> 00:04:32,610
