00:04:39,210 --> 00:04:42,330
hoc, you know, talk to your peer really quickly.

75
00:04:42,540 --> 00:04:47,760
The specs are kind of dated and wireframes can be really much more collaborative than that.

76
00:04:47,760 --> 00:04:50,550
So get your team involved as much as possible.

77
00:04:51,150 --> 00:04:53,070
The next thing is user testing.

78
00:04:53,280 --> 00:04:55,260
